All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.apache.wicket.IClusterable, org.apache.wicket.IConverterLocator, org.apache.wicket.markup.html.IHeaderPartContainerProvider
public abstract class ResponseEditor
extends org.apache.wicket.markup.html.panel.Panel

Base class for editing any type of response. This class handles the actual saving of a response. Override onSave(AjaxRequestTarget), onCancel(AjaxRequestTarget), and onDelete(AjaxRequestTarget) to provide additional behavior, such as redrawing a display. TODO: Does this need to be abstract? TODO: Add response limit options (upload, text length, recording length, etc).
